snippet: Prosecutors talked about a four-page to-do list that Sylvie Cachay gave Nicholas Brooks shortly before she was killed at the Soho House in 2010.
abstract: Prosecutors in murder trial of Nicholas Brooks present evidence demonstrating growing tumult of his six-month relationship with Sylvie Cachay, woman found dead in bathtub at exclusive Manhattan hotel; Brooks stands accused of strangling and drowning Cachay.
lead_paragraph: Prosecutors talked about a four-page to-do list that Sylvie Cachay gave Nicholas Brooks shortly before she was killed at the Soho House in 2010.

headline.seo: Jurors Hear of Turbulent Relationship in Sylvie Cachay Murder Trial
headline.main: At Murder Trial, Jurors Hear of Turbulent Relationship
